**What shipped:**
- Deleted `appendSessionLog` writer + caller in `sudd-go/internal/auto/runner.go`
- Deleted `sudd/memory/session-log.md` (file is retired — absence > pointer)
- Added `TestSessionLogIsAbsent` (4 subtests) + inverted the two existing zombie-sweep tests
- Stderr now prints a ✓ success line on zombie sweeps so operators still see them in `auto-reports/{date}/{change}.log`

**Proposal's literal "redirect to `auto-reports/{date}/summary.md`" was rejected** — that file is rewritten fresh each session and would lose mid-session appends. Rationale documented in archive's `specs.md` "Redirect decision" and `lessons.md`.

